    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-quality masterpiece. Every inch of the exterior gleams with its original high-gloss finish, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or even the slightest swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium Nappa leather seats show no bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent still lingers. This vehicle has been meticulously garage-kept and strictly maintained at the dealership, with a comprehensive folder of service records to prove its pampered life. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from a new vehicle\u2014the engine is whisper-quiet, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the tires are fresh. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the one. No accidents, one owner, and zero compromises.",
      "price": 46500.0,
