    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E36 M3 in impeccable factory specification. The S52B32 power unit exhibits flawless VANOS operation and robust compression across all six cylinders. Mated to a crisp ZF five-speed manual transmission and a 3.15 limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. The chassis is structurally sound with no evidence of subframe fatigue, riding on a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein B6 dampers and OEM bushings for original turn-in precision. Finished in its original Alpine White over a pristine black Nappa leather 'Vader' interior, this example retains all factory VIN tags and a comprehensive maintenance log. A truly turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
